[{"Code":"en","Title":"China Bank Online Banking","Slug":"china-bank-online-banking","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"023b09ea-cd7b-4045-a02e-4ece0c82a681\"><img data-block-id=\"17e8dcdc-883e-47bd-975e-e3e62bdbd9e3\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Chinabank-Logo.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"264\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:264px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"d6321c4d-03e7-434f-b38a-e83b3528f8d7\">China Banking Corporation (China Bank) is one of the oldest and most respected banks in the Philippines. Its digital platform, China Bank Online, provides customers with access to a variety of convenient banking services, including fund transfers, bill payments, and online purchases.</p><p data-block-id=\"a7a18cff-f6ba-4ef9-bf6e-ad9ca5a17a09\">This payment channel is primarily used by merchants who are offering our other online banking channels (with “ONLINE_BANKING” in the channel name).  You can also integrate directly with our China Bank direct debit channel.</p><hr class=\"hr-divider1\"><h2 data-block-id=\"6146dcc6-4245-4158-a034-de0971f8c50b\">Features</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"926\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:926px;width:926px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:463px;\"><col style=\"width:463px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"402452f7-7a96-45f3-856a-beec3466fb7a\">Channel Code</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"11cb345c-7d97-4a37-a184-08b5067a5ae1\">CHINABANK_ONLINE_BANKING</p><