045-a02e-4ece0c82a681\"><img data-block-id=\"17e8dcdc-883e-47bd-975e-e3e62bdbd9e3\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Chinabank-Logo.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt width=\"264\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:264px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"d6321c4d-03e7-434f-b38a-e83b3528f8d7\">China Banking Corporation (China Bank) เป็นหนึ่งในธนาคารที่เก่าแก่และได้รับการยอมรับมากที่สุดในประเทศฟิลิปปินส์ แพลตฟอร์มดิจิทัลของธนาคารคือ China Bank Online ซึ่งให้บริการลูกค้าด้วยบริการธนาคารที่สะดวกสบายหลากหลายรูปแบบ รวมถึงการโอนเงิน การชำระบิล และการซื้อสินค้าออนไลน์</p><p data-block-id=\"a7a18cff-f6ba-4ef9-bf6e-ad9ca5a17a09\">ช่องทางการชำระเงินนี้ส่วนใหญ่ใช้โดยร้านค้าที่ให้บริการช่องทางธนาคารออนไลน์อื่น ๆ ของเรา (ที่มีคำว่า “ONLINE_BANKING” อยู่ในชื่อช่องทาง) คุณยังสามารถเชื่อมต่อโดยตรงกับช่องทาง China Bank direct debit ของเราได้อีกด้วย</p><hr class=\"hr-divider1\"><h2 data-block-id=\"6146dcc6-4245-4158-a034-de0971f8c50b\">คุณสมบัติ</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"926\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:926px;width:926px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:463px;\"><col style=\"width:463px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"402452f7-7a96-45f3-856a-beec3466fb7a\">รหัสช่องทาง</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"11cb345c-7d97-4a37-a184-08b5067a5ae1\">CHINABANK_ONLINE_BANKING</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"e924926f-9906-4496-af4a-b319c2a2c8d4\">สกุลเงิน</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"89cc4585-3036-4f0a-847a-3a0f634c0a27\">PHP</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"6598736d-d850-48ae-b29e-ba649fb13157\">จำนวนเงินขั้นต่ำ</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"f5c1c704-b8ae-4d25-8fd5-2694332b973d\">1.00</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"93c4567d-ddd5-461c-8459-70cc0cce1024\">จำนวนเงินสูงสุด</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"182cd5d4-0077-4254-901f-9939ecae06f1\">1,000,000.00</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"73a8ce05-a222-44fb-b6c6-fa9069d5dfc4\">ขั้นตอนการอนุมัติของผู้ใช้</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"bb42dc08-4557-408e-985f-e98424855151\">REDIRECT</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"4888d640-07c9-4a08-aa89-fd2f705958bd\">บันทึก</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"de320cd4-3832-4edb-b65a-d9d2b0717696\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"d4dd8a87-001f-4750-954f-3b945aba5e48\">การชำระเงินซ้ำ</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"0a0ada44-cc78-4f92-b7e3-5d5f5fa029e6\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"1a306633-bbbe-4f04-bf87-db43583cea7b\">Auth &amp; Capture</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"ac9af3d4-f692-4f73-aedb-7a6a4908a9a2\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"6dafaffe-056c-47dd-9363-46082a9133f7\">Partial Capture</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"60a306e9-b83b-4b04-b5bd-07ffe7fe7665\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"dce8b2c9-f302-4b39-b28f-1629758eefff\">Multiple Partial Capture</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"fce61d55-92ed-4dca-a2a6-29fb90d2557d\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"0cf87f08-cadc-4646-83a5-749b7c38114e\">การหมดอายุของคำขอชำระเงิน (ชั่วโมง)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"a4bfae12-3af7-4be1-960f-9828b4252f1a\">1</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"87ed7ee5-1a1d-45b0-92d9-7d7737e62cf8\">ความถูกต้องของ Payment Token (ปี)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"68cffead-dea0-4e6c-8b72-99eca92d9b5e\"></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"ba0dce38-3f3e-49d7-ae0d-da0beca04eb7\">เวลาในการชำระบัญชี (ชั่วโมง)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"14e766a1-2c6e-480a-8f6b-6a62bb6258bf\">T+1 WORKING DAYS</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"94784d78-3f48-4267-bcfa-f5baf2381b19\">การคืนเงิน</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"323aad3c-8115-450e-9e69-5ddb6843d696\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"783f9060-f315-483c-b020-37f8079c7e5f\">Partial Refund</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"cf665411-2c95-4a5d-b9e9-0d3ec39cf64a\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"55cbaf83-ec18-4147-8950-585e0c4aaba7\">Multiple Partial Refund</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"957d2006-c589-4751-a1a0-174321a498e2\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"3795b679-c38a-4fae-88f4-7a3498c5b08e\">ความถูกต้องของการคืนเงิน (วัน)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"9f5634ea-ac19-47ae-9a88-b4b2d4a3d107\">N/A</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"d1760170-fa28-4c8b-b533-419100be3192\">การเชื่อมต่อที่เข้ากันได้</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"60823a34-d1b1-427e-90ab-60a877255f19\">Payment API, Payment Link</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"2b081c08-ffd2-493a-b253-c4931f5f1c75\">ขั้นตอนการชำระเงิน</h2><p data-block-id=\"3a86b5ec-38da-4400-83d2-ef1024cbe6c9\"></p><p data-block-id=\"12295416-ce37-4b1f-ae9c-e422707d5254\"></p><p data-block-id=\"8e9aac87-b7ff-4f0e-b9c9-0178d8f76e42\"></p><p data-block-id=\"1fba7422-3f0f-475f-a3cd-ed72e33bce4f\"></p><p data-block-id=\"acd97665-43b1-498b-89ca-e66b24c0a68f\"></p><p data-block-id=\"490a489a-2a58-4dc9-96ea-9e5cc09fc8be\"></p>","SeoTitle":"China Bank ออนไลน์แบงก์กิ้ง","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"China Bank Banca en Línea","Slug":"china-bank-online-banking","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"023b09ea-cd7b-4045-a02e-4ece0c82a681\"><img data-block-id=\"17e8dcdc-883e-47bd-975e-e3e62bdbd9e3\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Chinabank-Logo.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"264\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:264px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"d6321c4d-03e7-434f-b38a-e83b3528f8d7\">China Banking Corporation (China Bank) es uno de los bancos más antiguos y respetados de Filipinas. Su plataforma digital, China Bank Online, proporciona a los Clientes acceso a una variedad de servicios bancarios convenientes, incluyendo Transferencias de fondos, Pago de facturas y compras en línea.</p><p data-block-id=\"a7a18cff-f6ba-4ef9-bf6e-ad9ca5a17a09\">Este canal de Pago es utilizado principalmente por Comercios que ofrecen nuestros otros canales de banca en línea (con &#x201c;ONLINE_BANKING&#x201d; en el Nombre del canal). Usted también puede integrar directamente con nuestro canal de Direct Debit de China Bank.</p><hr class=\"hr-divider1\"><h2 data-block-id=\"6146dcc6-4245-4158-a034-de0971f8c50b\">Características</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"926\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:926px;width:926px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:463px;\"><col style=\"width:463px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"402452f7-7a96-45f3-856a-beec3466fb7a\">Código del Canal</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"11cb345c-7d97-4a37-a184-08b5067a5ae1\">CHINABANK_ONLINE_BANKING</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"e924926f-9906-4496-af4a-b319c2a2c8d4\">Moneda</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"89cc4585-3036-4f0a-847a-3a0f634c0a27\">PHP</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"6598736d-d850-48ae-b29e-ba649fb13157\">Monto Mínimo</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"f5c1c704-b8ae-4d25-8fd5-2694332b973d\">1.00</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"93c4567d-ddd5-461c-8459-70cc0cce1024\">Monto Máximo</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"182cd5d4-0077-4254-901f-9939ecae06f1\">1,000,000.00</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"73a8ce05-a222-44fb-b6c6-fa9069d5dfc4\">Flujo de Aprobación del Usuario</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"bb42dc08-4557-408e-985f-e98424855151\">REDIRECT</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"4888d640-07c9-4a08-aa89-fd2f705958bd\">Guardar</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"de320cd4-3832-4edb-b65a-d9d2b0717696\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding